ows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"中端单反新一代旗舰机 尼康D7100最新上市 \" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid\" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/112/261/ceJJpTyyWMyAg.jpg\" /><br />\r\n尼康D7100</p>\r\n<p sizset=\"false\" sizcache09747730509645729=\"4 11 187\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　在对焦方面，尼康D7100采用了51个对焦点，其中包含15个十字对焦点，这与尼康的旗舰单反<a class=\"hui14_line\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0)\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera/index226396.shtml\">D800</a>所采用的对焦系统一致，并且高于了全画幅单反<a class=\"hui14_line\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0)\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera/index322486.shtml\">D600</a>的39个对焦点。</p>\r\n<p sizset=\"false\" sizcache09747730509645729=\"4 11 187\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" borde