0000ff\" size=\"6\">&nbsp;</font></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/18066129/T2eqRmXmpNXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/18066129/T2IA9WXfXXXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/18066129/T2ZT5wXllbXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/18066129/T2bpSPXn4aXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/18066129/T2bqR6XdtdXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/18066129/T2e1qNXXJbXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: large\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: large\"><strong>关于托架里的4颗螺丝的使用：</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">买了托架的朋友询问，说托架不够稳固，有些晃动的问题。</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">如果仅仅把硬盘插到托架里面，随着托架的晃动，硬盘会有小幅度的位移</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: small\">这个好解决，硬盘的四周有4个螺丝孔，一个孔上一个螺丝</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/18066129/T20FOVXkXaXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/18066129/T2oT8AXllNXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-size: large\">我们可以看到托架内部有四个黑色的塑料凸起，此谓何物？</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #cc0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/18066129/T2nBmVXbBaXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">原来厂家早就为我们想好啦，预计到硬盘可能会松动，托架设</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">计了四个凸起，在硬盘四周上好四颗螺丝以后，然后再把硬盘</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">放到托架内，我们就会发现，那4颗螺丝正好会卡在那4个塑料</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">的突起处，这样，硬盘片再也不会出现晃动的现象啦</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/18066129/T2YuSWXcxaXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n用我们给您带的螺丝通过这2个孔降硬盘固定后就不会出现松动问题了</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><font color=\"#000000\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/18066129/T2gi9cXkxaXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.gif\" /></font></span></strong></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/18066129/T2s0xwXjJNXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/18066129/T24diWXihXXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/18066129/T2loKVXh0aXXXXXXXX_!!18066129.jpg\" /><img alt