=\"\" src=\"http://www.it567.com/uploadimg/arrow_grey.jpg\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" /></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255,102,0)\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span>模块化电路系统　电路保护技术，防止粉尘和磁化对电路的干扰，机器运行更稳定。<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102,102,102)\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.it567.com/uploadimg/arrow_grey.jpg\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" /></span></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255,102,0)\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>碎纸量控制系统　有效防止碎纸机堵、卡纸现象。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/24247039/T2faO3XopaXXXXXXXX_!!24247039.jpg\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; border-c